      <title>Steve Madden 以 3.6 亿美元收购英国鞋履品牌 Kurt Geiger</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/steve-madden-to-buy-uk-shoe-brand-kurt-geiger-for-360-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Steven Madden Ltd. 同意以约 2.89 亿英镑（3.6 亿美元）现金收购奢侈鞋类和时尚配饰品牌 Kurt Geiger Ltd.。]]></description>
