    <item>
      <title>英国债务主管认为创纪录的销售后到期期限是“最佳时机”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/uk-s-debt-chief-sees-maturity-sweet-spot-after-record-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国债务管理局似乎将继续向短期债券发行倾斜，以利用投资者对本周创纪录的 10 年期债券销售的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/uk-s-debt-chief-sees-maturity-sweet-spot-after-record-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 12:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀加剧导致美国债券价格上涨，创 12 月以来最差表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-bonds-rise-after-hot-inflation-fuels-worst-day-since-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债在经历了去年 12 月以来的最大抛售后小幅走高，因为投资者等待最新的通胀快照，以便从周三高于预期的通胀数据中寻找美国利率走势的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-bonds-rise-after-hot-inflation-fuels-worst-day-since-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2025 年欧洲股市有望上涨至 1 万亿美元，但持怀疑态度的投资者却蜂拥而至</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/skeptics-circle-european-stocks-after-1-trillion-rally-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管乌克兰战争结束谈判可能推动股市创下新高，但欧洲投资者开始怀疑该地区股市的火爆涨势还能持续多久。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/skeptics-circle-european-stocks-after-1-trillion-rally-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 08:59:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合利华选择阿姆斯特丹而非伦敦作为冰淇淋衍生品基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/unilever-sees-modest-profitability-boost-in-2025-starts-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合利华 (Unilever Plc) 表示，其冰淇淋部门将主要在阿姆斯特丹上市，而当 Ben &amp; Jerry’s 的生产商今年分拆后，伦敦和纽约将作为第二上市地点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/unilever-sees-modest-profitability-boost-in-2025-starts-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 07:12:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雀巢销售额增长加快，股价创 2009 年以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/nestle-sales-growth-exceeds-estimates-helped-by-higher-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大食品制造商雀巢公司 (Nestle SA) 的销售额在去年最后一个季度从历史最低水平回升，随后其股价出现 2009 年以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/nestle-sales-growth-exceeds-estimates-helped-by-higher-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 06:24:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税问题导致风险偏好减弱，美元缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/dollar-falls-as-trump-putin-talk-over-end-to-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，今日将实施对等关税，这抑制了市场对高风险资产的兴趣，并引发了人们对通胀可能进一步加速的担忧，随后美元缩减了跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/dollar-falls-as-trump-putin-talk-over-end-to-war-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 05:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
